  "content_markdown": "1\n\n###  Application and Definition\n\n1.1\n\nUnless otherwise stated, this Part applies to:\n\n  1. (1) a _UK Solvency II firm_ ;\n  2. (2) in accordance with [Insurance General Application 3](/pra-rules/insurance-general-application#2e5a9cd32e6d4026895a5d543b990108 \"Insurance General Application 3\"), the _Society_ , as modified by [5](/pra-rules/insurance---certification#7692905caa5747148ecca3b29d0bfbe3 \"5\");\n  3. (3) in accordance with [Insurance General Application 3](/pra-rules/insurance-general-application#2e5a9cd32e6d4026895a5d543b990108 \"Insurance General Application 3\"), a _managing agent_ , as modified by [5](/pra-rules/insurance---certification#7692905caa5747148ecca3b29d0bfbe3 \"5\");\n  4. (4) a _third country branch undertaking_ (other than a _Swiss general insurer_) in relation to the activities of the _third country branch_ that are subject to the _regulatory system_ ;\n  5. (4A) a _third country insurance services provider_ in relation to the activities carried out in the _UK_ that are subject to the _regulatory system_ ; and\n  6. (5) a _UK ISPV_ , in accordance with [6](/pra-rules/insurance---certification#738737821e6849678cc77dfd4f9d34b8 \"6\").\n\n*Effective: 31/12/2020*\n\n1.1A\n\nThis Part does not apply to a _SRO firm_.\n\n*Effective: 31/12/2020*\n\n1.2\n\nThis Part does not apply to a _small run-off firm_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n1.3\n\nIn this Part, the following definition shall apply:\n\n_employee_\n\nin relation to a _firm_ , includes any _person_ within the description set out in section 63E(9) of _FSMA_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n1.3A\n\nFor the purposes of this Part, _large firm_ includes a _third country insurance services provider_ which would be a _large firm_ if the amounts specified in (a) and (b) of the Glossary definition are only those amounts relating to the activities carried out in the _UK_ by the _third country insurance services provider_.\n\n*Effective: 31/12/2020*\n\n1.4\n\nThis Part does not apply to a function performed by:\n\n  1. (1) a _PRA approved person_ ;\n  2. (1A) a _person_ in relation to whom a notice under _section 59ZZA_ has been given to an _authorised person_ ;\n  3. (2) a _person_ who performs an _FCA controlled function_ ; or\n  4. (3) a _non-executive director_ in relation to their _non-executive director_ function.\n\n*Effective: 31/12/2020*\n\n2\n\n###  Certification Functions\n\n2.1\n\nFor the purposes of this Part, the following are _certification functions_ :\n\n  1. (1) a function performed for a _firm_ by a _key function holder_ at the _firm_ ;\n  2. (2) a function performed by a _material risk taker_ at a _large firm_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n2.2\n\nA function is only a _certification function_ to the extent that the function relates to a _regulated activity_ carried on by a _firm_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n3\n\n###  Performance of Certification Functions\n\n3.1\n\nA _firm_ must take reasonable care to ensure that none of its _employees_ performs a _certification function_ under an arrangement entered into by the _firm_ in relation to the carrying on by the _firm_ of a _regulated activity_ , unless the _employee_ has a valid _certificate_ issued by the _firm_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2019*\n\n3.2\n\nA _person_ does not perform a _certification function_ for a _firm_ under [2.1](/pra-rules/insurance---certification#6177f07795eb408ab53e11da8f678ea3 \"2.1\") if the _person_ is performing any _controlled function_ for that _firm_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n3.3\n\nTo the extent that:\n\n  1. (1) a firm appoints a _person_ to perform a function which, but for this rule, would be a _certification function_ ;\n  2. (2) the appointment is solely to provide cover for a _certification employee_ whose absence is reasonably unforeseen; and\n  3. (3) the appointment is for less than four weeks;\n\nsuch a _person_ does not perform a _certification function_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n4\n\n###  Material Risk Takers\n\n4.1\n\nThis Chapter applies to a _firm_ that falls within [1.1](/pra-rules/insurance---certification#ec0b8b0fc25b4a0cbba41308981a2b4a \"1.1\") and is a _large firm_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n4.2\n\nA _firm_ must identify, in respect of the _firm_ , its _employees_ who are _material risk takers_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n4.3\n\nA _firm_ must keep its identification of _material risk takers_ pursuant to [4.2](/pra-rules/insurance---certification#fbf9e3acb19b41248244e2cc62f538c6 \"4.2\") up-to-date.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n4.4\n\nA _firm_ must keep a record of its reasoning for the identification of _material risk takers_ pursuant to [4.2](/pra-rules/insurance---certification#fbf9e3acb19b41248244e2cc62f538c6 \"4.2\").\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n5\n\n###  Lloyd’s\n\n5.1\n\nThis Part applies to the _Society_ and _managing agents_ separately.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n6\n\n###  UK ISPVs\n\n6.1\n\n[2.1](/pra-rules/insurance---certification#6177f07795eb408ab53e11da8f678ea3 \"2.1\")(2) does not apply to a _UK ISPV_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n6.2\n\n[4](/pra-rules/insurance---certification#f3a31f4eefd242789847cf1deb8e42fa \"4\") does not apply to a _UK ISPV_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"col9\">\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"part-content\">\n\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"5ca5ac87f5504b17acf07103c9d0cff8\" id=\"59f69c7c67f44622b86734488ac8a9f5\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tApplication and Definition\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"3371ae83af2346c0a7b49a6aad99e754\" id=\"ec0b8b0fc25b4a0cbba41308981a2b4a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>Unless otherwise stated, this Part applies to:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52930\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-0d29d447fd4b4fca868c1d2e5b5e2276\" title=\"UK Solvency II firm\">UK Solvency II firm</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(2) in accordance with <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance-general-application#2e5a9cd32e6d4026895a5d543b990108\" title=\"Insurance General Application 3\">Insurance General Application 3</a>, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em>, as modified by <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification#7692905caa5747148ecca3b29d0bfbe3\" title=\"5\">5</a>;</li>\n<li>(3) in accordance with <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance-general-application#2e5a9cd32e6d4026895a5d543b990108\" style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\" title=\"Insurance General Application 3\">Insurance General Application 3</a>, a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52204\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-631b76adce9c4143ad8d33e593852c66\" title=\"managing agent\">managing agent</a></em>, as modified by <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification#7692905caa5747148ecca3b29d0bfbe3\" style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\" title=\"5\">5</a>;</li>\n<li>(4) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52916\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8241961260a4c6394b7710d6bf24e03\" title=\"third country branch undertaking\">third country branch undertaking</a></em> (other than a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52910\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7ecb61ce28ed4c4e947c300a772aa937\" title=\"Swiss general insurer\">Swiss general insurer</a></em>) in relation to the activities of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52915\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-233a78845cf54319a4301dbbfcea122c\" title=\"third country branch\">third country branch</a></em> that are subject to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52098\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8b88ef3d27fa45aeba6c11a8df1a92ac\" title=\"regulatory system\">regulatory system</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(4A) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"98245\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9620bcb18fb249d59d6b80a3d10010c6\" title=\"third country insurance services provider\">third country insurance services provider</a></em> in relation to the activities carried out in the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52122\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-f7844a8cbb824a52a26c043e3f6b584e\" title=\"UK\">UK</a></em> that are subject to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52098\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8b88ef3d27fa45aeba6c11a8df1a92ac\" title=\"regulatory system\">regulatory system</a></em>; and</li>\n<li>(5) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52386\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d657b35a131c4b4982032a800f337269\" title=\"UK ISPV\">UK ISPV</a></em>, in accordance with <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification#738737821e6849678cc77dfd4f9d34b8\" title=\"6\">6</a>.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification/10-12-2018#ec0b8b0fc25b4a0cbba41308981a2b4a\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.1 before 31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"165a96b0463e4e2988647e641d402c1d\" id=\"69d3406663b34e7ba61ac3aa525e7201\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.1A\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Part does not apply to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"98243\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-03d04f1c85064316998189ee87fa1eb0\" title=\"SRO firm\">SRO firm</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"8d75d6e90d4e4fae89bb289e99b6b13d\" id=\"8899a1d1018a46a4be23dde6ea6271c5\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Part does not apply to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"78129\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-dd26769b0dea4ec7b38d9b68fdd74943\" title=\"small run-off firm\">small run-off firm</a></em>. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"9f4054ef4e0043358864a8c7c8355195\" id=\"64456050287b41c4a409541619fe6632\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>In this Part, the following definition shall apply:</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88195\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9bb34bb69f38482fbd1df92e42a8f0f6\" title=\"employee\">employee</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">in relation to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>, includes any <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> within the description set out in section 63E(9) of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52115\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d7aa340192de4d37b63a54ba1489ac08\" title=\"FSMA\">FSMA</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"77f949b1e17449d29daf170bff2353df\" id=\"9f4f308035a84588b5238738abb37ef1\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.3A\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>For the purposes of this Part, <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88173\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-300cba9beefd454c86d4af543afbb709\" title=\"large firm\">large firm</a></em> includes a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"98245\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9620bcb18fb249d59d6b80a3d10010c6\" title=\"third country insurance services provider\">third country insurance services provider</a></em> which would be a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88173\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-300cba9beefd454c86d4af543afbb709\" title=\"large firm\">large firm</a></em> if the amounts specified in (a) and (b) of the Glossary definition are only those amounts relating to the activities carried out in the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52122\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-f7844a8cbb824a52a26c043e3f6b584e\" title=\"UK\">UK</a></em> by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"98245\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9620bcb18fb249d59d6b80a3d10010c6\" title=\"third country insurance services provider\">third country insurance services provider</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"e30aa4a071014364aeaf01aa27296010\" id=\"9a810d398388474d91f3fc9fa4e7df97\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.4\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Part does not apply to a function performed by:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52567\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9a4eb6e7bc0f455793dd9d3697399120\" title=\"PRA approved person\">PRA approved person</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(1A) a <em style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> in relation to whom a notice under <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"98241\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d4cdfb2b435742b7a2f0aef1d189bb13\" title=\"section 59ZZA\">section 59ZZA</a></em> has been given to an <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53233\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-2165460176e44a0b9cad0f898b857fb1\" title=\"authorised person\">authorised person</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(2) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> who performs an <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52565\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-4d084a65f6d6425f8b0dbef37e18160e\" title=\"FCA controlled function\">FCA controlled function</a></em>; or</li>\n<li>(3) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52566\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-1c6867ad63dc4c27b293a8dfdaf54393\" title=\"non-executive director\">non-executive director</a></em> in relation to their <em style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52566\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-1c6867ad63dc4c27b293a8dfdaf54393\" title=\"non-executive director\">non-executive director</a></em> function.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification/10-12-2018#9a810d398388474d91f3fc9fa4e7df97\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.4 before 31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"3477c945b70142e2ab3b846a1de8bcac\" id=\"56ec694462694c4a8a2ffce07b169ecd\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t2\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tCertification Functions\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"34752ef6c9c94fef9e216d3b4343e300\" id=\"6177f07795eb408ab53e11da8f678ea3\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>For the purposes of this Part, the following are <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52563\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-82074f76e19f49a5b684450294320fee\" title=\"certification functions\">certification functions</a></em>: </p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) a function performed for a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> by a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52842\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-fd5d0277f5e14a8ea81a9cb3889733d4\" title=\"key function holder\">key function holder</a></em> at the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(2) a function performed by a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88188\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-150b6dbee6a848ed9caa25d672011c95\" title=\"material risk taker\">material risk taker</a></em> at a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88173\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-300cba9beefd454c86d4af543afbb709\" title=\"large firm\">large firm</a></em>.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"e63b7562a0b844dbbedaf489d18c50c8\" id=\"dec9ab92bdc241d5a049983c29f2f778\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A function is only a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52563\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-82074f76e19f49a5b684450294320fee\" title=\"certification function\">certification function</a></em> to the extent that the function relates to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77616\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-aa04e0522d234dabb44ae6041cd9954b\" title=\"regulated activity\">regulated activity</a></em> carried on by a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"c4e659e982484c8297b249fde50e85b1\" id=\"3279ccb5640b48448bf1e0c9df3fea05\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t3\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tPerformance of Certification Functions\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"5b09052a19f3438bb5c544a6f93fb56b\" id=\"9a4debc43df24257bebd9a32308a4dff\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must take reasonable care to ensure that none of its <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88195\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9bb34bb69f38482fbd1df92e42a8f0f6\" title=\"employees\">employees</a></em> performs a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52563\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-82074f76e19f49a5b684450294320fee\" title=\"certification function\">certification function</a></em> under an arrangement entered into by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> in relation to the carrying on by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> of a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77616\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-aa04e0522d234dabb44ae6041cd9954b\" title=\"regulated activity\">regulated activity</a></em>, unless the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88195\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9bb34bb69f38482fbd1df92e42a8f0f6\" title=\"employees\">employee</a></em> has a valid <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52562\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7d8c159526f2426b93d818990ce5ea47\" title=\"certificate\">certificate</a></em> issued by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2019\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification/10-12-2018#9a4debc43df24257bebd9a32308a4dff\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 3.1 before 10/12/2019\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"9f9194f71b5649ea96df4ebf8811f20d\" id=\"d4b1726322554244a895c4c99f6de0be\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> does not perform a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52563\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-82074f76e19f49a5b684450294320fee\" title=\"certification function\">certification function</a></em> for a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> under <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification#6177f07795eb408ab53e11da8f678ea3\" title=\"2.1\">2.1</a> if the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> is performing any <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52215\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-77ed05e95e9144549fdcd84ae397fcab\" title=\"controlled function\">controlled function</a></em> for that <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"9dd3ded7b05445898e86773f4ed6f045\" id=\"a6c347c6d58545bcbb2596bd48733a47\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>To the extent that:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) a <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a> appoints a <em style=\"text-indent: 0px;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> to perform a function which, but for this rule, would be a <em style=\"text-indent: 0px;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52563\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-82074f76e19f49a5b684450294320fee\" title=\"certification function\">certification function</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(2) the appointment is solely to provide cover for a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52564\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-f42fcd52d02845298b099cb7f4c95ed8\" title=\"certification employee\">certification employee</a></em> whose absence is reasonably unforeseen; and</li>\n<li>(3) the appointment is for less than four weeks;</li>\n</ol>\n<p>such a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> does not perform a<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52563\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-82074f76e19f49a5b684450294320fee\" title=\"certification function\">certification function</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"e43af43974b547a69c9cbaaeddcf8b63\" id=\"f3a31f4eefd242789847cf1deb8e42fa\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t4\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tMaterial Risk Takers\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"2a6f15f0960c4ec79099ae8275386655\" id=\"2a43294c737d43589668e7a79bb7984f\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Chapter applies to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> that falls within <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification#ec0b8b0fc25b4a0cbba41308981a2b4a\" title=\"1.1\">1.1</a> and is a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88173\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-300cba9beefd454c86d4af543afbb709\" title=\"large firm\">large firm</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"d40dd20caf674dca9db17f12b648f327\" id=\"fbf9e3acb19b41248244e2cc62f538c6\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must identify, in respect of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>, its <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88195\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-9bb34bb69f38482fbd1df92e42a8f0f6\" title=\"employees\">employees</a></em> who are <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88188\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-150b6dbee6a848ed9caa25d672011c95\" title=\"material risk takers\">material risk takers</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"0f6e83337ecd4569be6d60b2a99196ee\" id=\"0e7ae565f56f4efe8264e8a26bcdac94\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must keep its identification of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88188\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-150b6dbee6a848ed9caa25d672011c95\" title=\"material risk takers\">material risk takers</a></em> pursuant to <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification#fbf9e3acb19b41248244e2cc62f538c6\" title=\"4.2\">4.2</a> up-to-date.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"13c7a41de4b84f37b45ae723b035c210\" id=\"dfd747ea2c304045810649fc81e28c26\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.4\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must keep a record of its reasoning for the identification of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88188\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-150b6dbee6a848ed9caa25d672011c95\" title=\"material risk takers\">material risk takers</a></em> pursuant to <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification#fbf9e3acb19b41248244e2cc62f538c6\" title=\"4.2\">4.2</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"204f9aeeed4149a5ba34868e94d39298\" id=\"7692905caa5747148ecca3b29d0bfbe3\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t5\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tLloyd’s\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"ee467286f1424457a2cd2fef913f69c9\" id=\"b375b3c5fa004dd0aa7080d249ee67d5\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t5.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Part applies to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em> and <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52204\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-631b76adce9c4143ad8d33e593852c66\" title=\"managing agents\">managing agents</a></em> separately. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"b0dcd9ee08cc406c9d169e19b2145ca3\" id=\"738737821e6849678cc77dfd4f9d34b8\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t6\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tUK ISPVs\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"3c06fc8696bc4aff895194266b4b56f6\" id=\"5ffc373a5f9240f487550e178c143811\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t6.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification#6177f07795eb408ab53e11da8f678ea3\" title=\"2.1\">2.1</a>(2) does not apply to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52386\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d657b35a131c4b4982032a800f337269\" title=\"UK ISPV\">UK ISPV</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"712105df7394496bbf1982700bee2e90\" id=\"3ea0928758c04b6a9d3d3d12e7919c32\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t6.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification#f3a31f4eefd242789847cf1deb8e42fa\" title=\"4\">4</a> does not apply to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52386\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d657b35a131c4b4982032a800f337269\" title=\"UK ISPV\">UK ISPV</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div>",
  "raw_sha256": "7a747082abc40607e13274b894f8943d2dcefd401090f24ed1a55808a238036b",
  "canonical_json_path": null
}